profile:
Rite-Way Fencing Inc. has been serving clients throughout Western Canada for over 30 years and is one of Canadaâ€™s largest fencing companies.
There are currently 10 Rite-Way Fencing locations in British Columbia, Alberta, and Saskatchewan with over 150 employees and 50 installation crews.
We provide fencing for private homes, business owners, large-scale commercial and industrial projects, government institutions, community facilities, recreation and sports facilities, farms and acreages.
Each location also provides rental and temporary fencing requirements and carries fence construction packages for the Do-It-Yourself enthusiast.
service_area: Calgary (Head Office): Airdrie, Cochrane, High River, Banff, Drumheller, Okotoks, Invermere, Golden, Strathmore, Canmore Edmonton: Bonnyville, Fort McMurray, Lloydminster, Camrose, ...
products: We have a wide range of residential fencing products including chain-link fencing, ornamental iron fencing, wood fencing, and vinyl/PVC fencing. We have a selection of privacy fence inserts (or privacy slats) and we supply portable dog kennels (or dog runs). Rite-Way Fencing Inc. also provides a wide variety of gates along with electric gate operators and access control systems.
services: We provide fencing packages and parts for all types of fencing.  We can install it for you, or you can do-it-yourself.
specialities: We manufacture high-quality chain-link fencing products to suit any size of project. Each of our locations has a welding shop capable of producing a wide variety of gates and portable dog kennels (or dog runs). We are also a distributor of ornamental iron fencing, wood fencing, vinyl/PVC fencing, gate automation and access control systems, and privacy fence inserts (or privacy slats).
memberships: American Fence Association (AFA), Chain Link Fence Manufacturers Institute (CLFMI)
warranty_terms: Varies depending on product, but generally one year from install date
